title: Study Music Project Playlist (53 Songs)
description:
In 2012, I uploaded a Study Music Project Playlist with the 26 songs that were then available. Since then, Dr. Dennis Kuo has added numerous songs to his repertoire for us to enjoy and study with. 

There is a wonderful YouTube playlist available with all of these songs and song 1-2 compilations, but sometimes we are without internet and it's nice to have the hard copy.

Enjoy and share the word!
